02:21.342 --> 02:24.971
Family is everything, no?

02:25.062 --> 02:28.213
Now, do you love your son?

02:29.622 --> 02:31.101
Si.

02:39.302 --> 02:42.772
Now, do you understand?

02:43.822 --> 02:48.054
You have a $10 million insurance policy.
I know that.

02:48.582 --> 02:49.981
Follow these instructions

02:50.222 --> 02:52.611
or God be with your child.

02:53.102 --> 02:54.421
You will remove your shirt

02:54.502 --> 02:56.538
