- Yes, I have.

01:39:25.265 --> 01:39:27.256
- You know what it is?
- Yes.

01:39:27.385 --> 01:39:29.580
I'm the president of La Hermandad.

01:39:29.665 --> 01:39:30.984
- You're the president?
- Yes.

