02:04:48.545 --> 02:04:52.743
He left the roof. We lost the signal.

02:04:52.825 --> 02:04:54.304
We got cut off.

02:04:56.145 --> 02:04:57.897
We lost him. We lost him.

02:05:00.105 --> 02:05:01.015
Damn.

