02:06:37.785 --> 02:06:39.343
Here.

02:06:40.345 --> 02:06:42.984
I'm goin' up on the bridge to get Pita.

02:06:43.065 --> 02:06:47.183
Anything goes wrong, you put it to his head,

02:06:47.265 --> 02:06:50.223
